narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Hindi is a pretty easy class. It's taught by three professors, who are often on different pages about the course material, so it's never really clear what work you need to do or hand in. There is a close group of students who take it, but the amount of Hindi you will learn is pretty minimal.
I would recommend this class for anyone continuing from L1/L2 last year.
Teachers are kind, class is fun, language is beautiful!
